OL,3,CFather who carries disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs waiting seven months for
OL,5,Csuitable home
OL,7,FITV News' Elaine Willcox paid a visit
OL,8,Fto Stephen's home to see how the
OL,9,Fcramped conditions are affecting his
OL,10,Ffamily.
OL,12,FA father-of-four who has to carry his
OL,13,Fdisabled son up flights of stairs
OL,14,Fmultiple times a day says it's
OL,15,Fimpossible to give "his children a
OL,16,Fbetter life" until they find a
OL,17,Fsuitable home.
