OL,3,CFather who carries disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs waiting seven months for
OL,5,Csuitable home
OL,7,FStephen Murray currently lives with
OL,8,Fhis four sons in his one bedroom flat
OL,9,Fin Widnes, where they are all forced
OL,10,Fto sleep in the same room.
OL,12,FIn their bedroom, Stephen explains: In
OL,13,F(one) bed is Kade and Kaylum, and the
OL,14,Fone that's folded up is where my
OL,15,Feighteen year old Kyle sleeps. But my
OL,16,Fmum passed away on Mother's Day so
OL,17,Fhe's sleeping at my dad's at the
OL,18,Fmoment.
OL,26,@uD@ApmuD@Epn
