OL,3,CFather who carries disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs waiting seven months for
OL,5,Csuitable home
OL,7,FThe pain from his legs can cause Harry
OL,8,Fto cry out in pain, much to the
OL,9,Fdistress of his brothers.
OL,11,FHis older brother Kade said: "I love
OL,12,F(Harry). I love him with all my heart,
OL,13,Fand I want him to be happy but right
OL,14,Fnow he can't be happy because he can't
OL,15,Fget what he needs."
OL,17,FHis other brother Kaylum added: "What
OL,18,Fif my dad falls? What would happen
OL,19,Fthen with Harry? All we need is a
OL,20,Fhouse with enough bedrooms for us."
