OL,3,CFather who carries disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs waiting seven months for
OL,5,Csuitable home
OL,7,FTheir father Stephen has been
OL,8,Fsearching for a suitable home for
OL,9,Fseven months, and despite successfully
OL,10,Fbidding on three properties all of the
OL,11,Foffers were eventually withdrawn. He
OL,12,Fworries that even when he does find a
OL,13,Fnew home, his housing association
OL,14,FHalton Housing will not pay for the
OL,15,Fadaptations needed to help Harry.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
