OL,3,CFather who carries disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs waiting seven months for
OL,5,Csuitable home
OL,7,FIn response, Halton Housing said:
OL,8,F"Since being made aware of Mr Murray's
OL,9,Fchange of circumstances, we've been
OL,10,Fworking closely with him to support a
OL,11,Fmove to a more suitable home that will
OL,12,Fmeet his family's needs."
OL,14,FBut Stephen's local MP Derek Twigg
OL,15,Fsays he is "very unhappy" with Halton
OL,16,FHousing's response, claiming there is
OL,17,Fno "adequate explanation given" about
OL,18,Fthe withdrawals of previous offers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
