OL,3,CFather who carries disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs waiting seven months for
OL,5,Csuitable home
OL,7,FHe said: "Halton Housing advised that
OL,8,Fthere was no date available for when
OL,9,Fthis family will be adequately housed
OL,10,Fand no adequate explanation given
OL,11,Fabout why the previous house offer was
OL,12,Fwithdrawn.
OL,14,F"Halton Housing have been informed
OL,15,Fthat I am very unhappy with their
OL,16,Fresponse, I have asked for further
OL,17,Fassistance for Mr Murray and his
OL,18,Fchildren."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
