OL,5,Csuitable home
OL,7,FUntil a suitable home is found,
OL,8,FStephen will have to continue carrying
OL,9,Fhis son up a narrow hallway at least
OL,10,Ftwice a day.
OL,12,FHe said: "People have said 'what would
OL,13,Fhappen if you hurt your back? Well I'd
OL,14,Fbe knackered wouldn't I? What am I
OL,15,Fmeant to do? I've got to carry him
OL,16,Fupstairs or we sleep in my car."
